  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "Synthetic adversarial V&V 40 credibility package for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is constructed to trigger weakener W-AR-02: the hasDecisionRecord outcome is Accepted while one CredibilityFactor (Model form) carries an achievedLevel strictly below its requiredLevel. All other factors are assessed at or above required levels. The justification language in the decision rationale is deliberately plausible-sounding but does not formally close the structural gap.",
